ated to business and development activities\r\nIntegrate educational and research activities to income generation and vice versa\r\nEstablish systems of efficient resource utilization culture in the university\r\nInitiate, coordinate and support the establishment of enterprises (income generating firms) by the university\r\nFollow up the quality of services provided by the directorates under the VPBD\r\nOrganize teams that could develop university wide income generating projects\r\nHandles media briefings related to activities of the process\r\nEndorse and sign different Memorandum of Understanding with concerned partners.\r\nAdvertise the capacity of the university in providing services in terms of the available staff members and infrastructure\r\nPerforms any other duty as deemed necessary.', '2015-06-04 22:13:11');

